PyWiki2Xhtml : Python module for wiki transform operations.

This was originally a translation of the original PHP class Wiki2xhtml in 
Python.

Instance the class and use his tranform() method to perform a tranformation
of plain text with wiki markup into Xhtml.

The class has an help() object to display a help text on the wiki syntax.

